esla OTA Software Update都俾人話非法改裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:56:19.000Z","msg":"但係好多日本行貨車都開哂 CarPlay 同 auto，<br />\n<br />\n問1823就答咗呢堆嘢，但睇唔明點解得VW唔合格<br />\n<br />\n「 根據《道路交通(車輛構造及保養)規例》香港法例第374A章第37條規定；汽車上可安裝為向駕駛人提供下述資料或視景而設計的視象顯示器： <br />\n(a)        關於該汽車或其他裝備的現況的資料； <br />\n(b)        該汽車任何部分或該汽車四周範圍當時的閉路式視景； <br />\n(c)        關於該汽車當時所處位置的資料；或 <br />\n(d)        其他只供用於該汽車導航的資料 <br />\n<br />\n汽車代理商在進口車輛到本港時，會要求車輛製造商對該視象顯示器的部份顯示功能進行刪除，以達到上述法例要求，方可通過類型評定審批。 」"},{"pid":"7a64b7f13d88af8cfced4f42ee89cd00274f0b00","tid":1615724,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"因為要收你五千"},{"pid":"2ec66e827ed42ffb604f4d575bb27e2dae345eb2","tid":1615724,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:06:58.000Z","msg":"sales =dog"},{"pid":"f9d1e5471ae54c8ed7683e0c307ee80473d93158","tid":1615724,"uid":97240,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T21:48:53.000Z","msg":"2019 年APPLE CARPLAY/ANDROID AUTO 都要加錢你叫佢食屎啦"},{"pid":"e02414efca3acda48022dab915016d7aae689b6f","tid":1615724,"uid":329544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9d1e5471ae54c8ed7683e0c307ee80473d93158","tid":1615724,"uid":97240,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T21:48:53.000Z","msg":"2019 年APPLE CARPLAY/ANDROID AUTO 都要加錢你叫佢食屎啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:10:26.000Z","msg":"佢仲要話係佢搵到方法幫我加，<br />\n又開咗之後架車又會無保養"},{"pid":"98d51ee126daccba816f2054169aecb3834464f1","tid":1615724,"uid":59046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:58:56.000Z","msg":"Carplay ios13 好正"},{"pid":"f0fd5374472da7981689fa0ffce81517f2ab752e","tid":1615724,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98d51ee126daccba816f2054169aecb3834464f1","tid":1615724,"uid":59046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:58:56.000Z","msg":"Carp